text: Islamgulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Araslanovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Meleuz, 4 km from Smakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Islamgulovo
